    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a good-condition car. Buyers can expect a well-maintained example that presents nicely and drives reliably. The exterior shows minor signs of normal use \u2014 small scratches here and there and perhaps a light scuff or two \u2014 but no significant dents, rust, or paint damage. The interior is clean and comfortable, with modest wear on high-contact areas like the driver's seat and steering wheel, but no tears, stains, or broken components. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been kept up with regular maintenance; all major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and cooling \u2014 are in good working order. Tires have reasonable tread remaining. This is a solid, dependable vehicle for a buyer looking for reliable daily transportation without paying mint-condition prices.",
      "price": 34000.0,
