      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid & Dependable \u2014 A Practical Choice at a Great Price! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it's a real, working car that gets you where you need to go without the premium price tag! The exterior shows some visible wear including minor scratches and small dents consistent with everyday use, so it's not going to win any beauty contests, but it has honest, real-world character. The interior is functional with some wear on the seats and surfaces, as you'd expect from a well-used vehicle. Mechanically, it runs and drives, making it a smart pick for a budget-conscious buyer who needs reliable transportation. No false promises here \u2014 just a straightforward, usable car at a fair price. Come take it for a spin and see if it's the right fit for you!",
